3. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - Genetic algorithms and particle swarm optimization are also commonly used in evolutionary computing. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - Fuzzy inference systems are often used in control systems and this paper discusses optimization methods for them.
